A Sticky Note Drawing


I am a junior Biology major and Computer Science minor at UMass Amherst. My interests include genetics, cellular & molecular biology, and bioinformatics. Currently, I am a TA for BIO311 General Genetics. Some of my hobbies are badminton, drawing, and video games.
